graph TB
    subgraph "Data Science Pipelines Operator"
        Controller[DSPO Controller Manager<br/>Reconciles DSPA CRs]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>Validation]
    end

    subgraph "DSP Instance Components (per namespace)"
        APIServer[API Server<br/>8888/HTTP, 8887/gRPC, 8443/HTTPS]
        PersistenceAgent[Persistence Agent<br/>Syncs workflow status]
        ScheduledWF[Scheduled Workflow Controller<br/>Cron pipelines]
        WorkflowController[Workflow Controller<br/>Argo v2 only]
        MLMD[ML Metadata gRPC<br/>8080/gRPC]
        MLMDEnvoy[ML Metadata Envoy Proxy<br/>9090/gRPC mTLS]
        UI[ML Pipelines UI<br/>Optional, dev/test only]
        MariaDB[MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP<br/>Optional built-in]
        Minio[Minio<br/>9000/TCP<br/>Optional built-in]
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| DSPA[DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR]
    DSPA -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|deploys| APIServer
    Controller -->|deploys| PersistenceAgent
    Controller -->|deploys| ScheduledWF
    Controller -->|deploys v2| WorkflowController
    Controller -->|deploys optional| MLMD
    Controller -->|deploys optional| MLMDEnvoy
    Controller -->|deploys optional| UI
    Controller -->|deploys optional| MariaDB
    Controller -->|deploys optional| Minio

    APIServer -->|stores metadata| MariaDB
    APIServer -->|tracks lineage| MLMD
    PersistenceAgent -->|updates status| MariaDB
    MLMD -->|persists to| MariaDB
    MLMDEnvoy -->|proxies| MLMD

    APIServer -->|creates workflows| WorkflowController
    APIServer -->|creates workflows| Tekton[Tekton Pipelines<br/>DSP v1]
    WorkflowController -->|executes| PipelinePod[Pipeline Pods]
    Tekton -->|executes| PipelinePod

    PipelinePod -->|stores artifacts| Minio
    PipelinePod -->|stores artifacts| S3[External S3 Storage]
    PipelinePod -->|reports status| APIServer

    %% External Dependencies
    Controller -->|depends on| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]
    Controller -->|optional| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>TLS provisioning]
    Controller -->|integrates| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>mTLS, network policies]

    %% ODH Integration
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI management| APIServer
    Prometheus[Prometheus Operator] -->|scrapes metrics| Controller

